          </p>

          <h3>Mainland Courts (Arabic Required)</h3>

          <p>
            <a href="/legal/litigation/">Dubai Courts</a>, Abu Dhabi Judicial Department, Sharjah Courts, and all Federal Courts operate exclusively in Arabic. Every foreign-language document—whether evidence, contracts, or judgments—must be submitted with <a href="/legal-translation-dubai/">MOJ-certified Arabic translation</a>.
          </p>

